VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT NODE_ENV\s*=\s*[\'\"]development[\'\"]|debug\s*:\s*true|logger\(\s*[\'\"]dev[\'\"]
WHEN EXPR MISSING:release|production
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects development/debug settings in potentially deployable paths.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Vue Debug/Verbose Mode Enabled.
